class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\CommandHandlerRegistry"
type: final class
summary: The CommandHandlerRegistry acts as a central lookup mechanism for resolving command handlers by their specific kind. It maintains a registry of handler instances to facilitate efficient dispatching within the application's command handling pipeline.
